{"title": "'Neighbour from hell' drove 6 families away from Punggol HDB block", "tags": "singapore", "timestamp": "2019-06-23", "content": "Over the past two years, one Housing Board block in Punggol has seen heavy market activity. Six households on the same floor moved out - because of one woman.\nDubbed the neighbour from hell, she is accused of splashing oil at others' doors, playing loud music and stomping on the floor. One neighbour even claimed she had left a bloody pig's ear on a shoe rack."}